Subject: Ohio Buses n Boats Event only 1 week to go

Howdy Y'all,
This will be the last reminder sent for the Third
Annual VW Buses, Boats, n Bands Event held just North
of Cincinnati Ohio next weekend, May 16-18. The event
is put on by the Ohio Valley Tribe of the Full Moon
Bus Club. It will feature camping, an eight mile canoe
trip on the Little Miami River, LIVE music in the
campground, door prizes, and of course the World
Famous Full Moon Bus club Breakfast Burritos.
Here is the official web site link:
http://www.geocities.com/buses_n_boats
We are expecting folks from as far away as Maryland,
New York, and Canada, as well as many people from the
immediate surrounding states. Come on out and
experience some of that Good Ole' Midwestern Hospitality.

=====
Peace, John Baker
1971 Westy
1972 Deluxe
